Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.91,0:00:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二局
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等下啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.97,0:00:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好  武禮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起呀  武禮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎  能不能讓我也來比一場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  但剛才你說我們再比也沒什麼意義…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算啦  我是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去拿護具
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒在說你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:00:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  武…武禮…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.27,0:01:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江高中一年級  川添珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.31,0:01:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是石橋賢三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.86,0:01:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添珠姬  與我一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:58.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第7話\N壽司與炸肉餅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一決勝負？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊  武禮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對吧～你不是吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是先鋒川添珠姬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:19.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這種地步你還…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是練習賽  再加上我們的交情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人身兼二職我也就不說你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不給你準備時間就提出要比賽也是我不對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人身兼二職？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊前輩？我完全聽不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我差不多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  比賽按照這個結果就行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要約定要看我與川添珠姬比賽的結果而定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩…你那麼想要獎盃嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎盃…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  說起來還有這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:03:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那麼想和小珠…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:03:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看她  你什麼都感覺不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在不比一場  我是平靜不下來的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何！要不要和我比一場！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  小珠  你自己決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩他很強  是很好的練習機會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的不對  小次郎  我不是強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今我都沒有停止練習過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是比以前更強了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啦  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  你也覺得不過癮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家想看小珠比賽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打啦  和大人打打看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那我接受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:10.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}川添珠姬 對 石橋賢三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣！幹掉她！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師！好好關照我的敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  勞您費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都很辛苦呢  被老師耍得團團轉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會不會  這也會成為學習經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就由我和勇次來做裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  小次郎  我硬要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管放手一戰吧  珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 小珠～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  可不能莽撞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想殺了小珠啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！竟然打飛了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你太過火了！對方又不是男生！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不認真打馬上就會被得分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…為什麼會提出自己上場的要求呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人…總會有被無法抑制的衝動所支配的時候啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好成熟！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人好成熟！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:06:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼…改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起！這種程度也不過才高一嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起！如此了不起的集中力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當下這傢伙的眼睛裡根本看不到周圍的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到的只有我的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種才能…這股集中力…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那時的我有這樣的才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我不集中精神搞什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過怎麼說也不會輸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟男女體格有別  體力相差太遠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何況手臂長度差太多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不能打贏大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太輕  不算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那樣不算嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是女生再加上單手  給人感覺力道不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且單手本來就不怎麼容易拿到分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了  一般女生也不會用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師是笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准對我的公平裁判有怨言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不服氣嗎  小珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這種事情分散注意力…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然還是小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露出破綻了  到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手拔擊單手擊面！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太帥了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是頭一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:09:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是小珠的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效  沒有異議
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有點糟糕…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說我就要這麼輸掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定他！小珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然身材矮小  卻已經是出色的劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩開始認真了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是小珠恐怕也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個架勢是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是上段  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師擺出上段…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是頭一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連和男生練習都沒有用過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我見識一下吧！小珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠認真起來的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見識一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講笑話  請到上段道場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:20.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（日文諧音冷笑話…）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你發什麼呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？我一擺出上段她的集中力一下就斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思…突然提出了奇怪的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連賽三場也累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚去吃壽司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為紀念我們的相識請嘗嘗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我家店裡做的炸肉餅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  正好肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  橫尾你不是才因為吃太多而肚子疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一運動就消化啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃～！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉餡味道十足  外皮的硬度也正好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  大家也來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子都餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要我要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:30.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  小珠也別客氣  請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管拿  你打了那麼多場  肚子早餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說不出口…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人已經偷偷吃過飯團了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小珠比了三場  所以要吃三個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家做的炸肉餅就算冷掉也很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  也給我一個啊  我說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活動過身體後的食物真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫尾你不是被秒殺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也輸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來  我們取勝的只有淺川一個人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊  去死好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪我上松高一趟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松本高中嗎  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說進來了個很厲害的新人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊  這勁頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來一次嗎  在這種時代其他學校的人去踢館
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.53,0:14:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！小次郎！理解我的就只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！我們走！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去踢館！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢館啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們  快點吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次來附近的時候  記得上我們家店裡玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你們算便宜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小次郎  晚上見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果獎盃還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你收著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.36,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}抱歉！\N今天還是見不了面了！\N<(  )>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種傢伙…那種傢伙…那種傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.73,0:15:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:15:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好送你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我從老家帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是動畫迷就絕對無法釋手的逸品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你大概會喜極而泣的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！一定會的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,VideoDisk？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,VHD？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來說明！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂VHD是1983發行的影像光碟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:26.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Video High-Density Disc：高密度視頻盤)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於其低廉的價格與出色的播放能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與LD一同受到收藏家們的重視
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並常作為發售偶像以及動畫典藏版的傳說中的載體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放不進去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做功課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壽司壽司  我喜歡～我喜歡～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是壽司王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  吃啊  小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是鮭魚子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正宗江戶前壽司呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩老爸開的正宗！江戶前！不回轉壽司店呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  倒閉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是小有名氣的店了  怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過那已經不是老爸的店了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉讓給別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人來到店裡不過四年就把老爸的手藝學的一分不差
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了老爸和常客  就連原本要繼承店鋪的大哥都認同了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼可以把這間店交付給他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸他安心地退下一線  大哥也自願退出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:18:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管在哪裡都有天才啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管咧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的約定呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年免費吃到飽呢？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定上說是老爸的店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才說要快點比嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你太拖泥帶水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！把鮭魚子還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說你知道會這樣才說讓我吃一年的壽司嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知馬上就不是你老爸的店了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你「唔」了吧？你剛才「唔」了一下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好卑鄙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來約定都是在騙人！ 根本是幻想！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！現在我帶你來吃回轉壽司你還不感謝我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了嗎  我還有在另一家學校教劍道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過的吧  現在兼任兩所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！你這什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼也就是說練習賽的對手有兩所學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.68,0:18:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩邊不能全部取勝的話約定就不成立嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  側身肉、蝦和沙丁魚各來一份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  沙丁魚已經沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那點什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎  你有什麼想吃的可以叫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙！回答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為想不怎麼可能  所以隨口作了約定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙小人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪裡有資格說我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這樣會打擾到其他客人…請安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒資格說我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添珠姬啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她根本是超實力級別的嘛！你從哪個道場搶來的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是搶來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是掉下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從天上…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你說她？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是教導主任…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才聽得懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之讓那樣的人戰兩場根本是犯規啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當半斤八兩  我就屈尊忍耐一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  請給我黑鮪肚、長鰭鯖、牡丹蝦跟…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！這些全都是525元一盤的東西啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我節制一點！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有今天了啊！我只有今天能吃了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳底磨破皮了  走路都疼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你加入劍道部了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係  很合適你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  我肚子餓了  做飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你耳背啊？我說走路都疼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法了  姐姐我好久也沒下廚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通心粉？義大利蔬菜湯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好有雞蛋  那就做蛋炒飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再受到打擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.66,0:21:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你坐我DS上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來啦！起來啦姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和彥你做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯好了  走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然熬夜做大家的練習進度表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真是有部長樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且大家的都還各自獨立
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長 is Great！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘了外山和岩佐的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視…忘了關
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.82,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:27.84,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:34.23,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:55.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.74,0:23:02.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:10.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:17.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:20.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:25.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:32.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:35.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:40.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:48.05,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.82,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:27.84,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中閃耀著的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:34.23,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:55.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗邊光著腳丫  仰望著夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.74,0:23:02.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有無法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:10.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮現出午時的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:17.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒勞得令人著急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:20.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:25.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}閉上眼睛傾聽心中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:32.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然無法得知  它想與我相見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:35.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:40.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光輝而耀眼的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:48.05,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.98,0:23:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是勇次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  上次小次郎老師因為時間緣故  詞語接龍沒有說完的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.84,0:23:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次由我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.36,0:24:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真是沒用的大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.93,0:24:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「バ」  啪的一聲擊中面部
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.77,0:24:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ン」  即使被抱怨膚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ブ」  讓人私下抱怨不停
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.56,0:24:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「レ」  也只求一心練習
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.34,0:24:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  也算完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集是「小珠和打工」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.03,0:24:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預告中終於看到了那個人的登場！
